---
title: Retro gaming reviews, news and articles
description: Retro Delights has retro gaming news, is a place to learn about retro gaming and retro products to collect.
layout: home-base.njk
templateEngineOverride: md, njk
---


<div class="grid-pacman">
  <div class="intro">
      <h1>Retro games delight</h1>

    <p class="highlight">The number 1 place for retro gaming and products.</p>
    <p>We're on a journey to become the UK's leading retro gaming website. Our passion is retro gaming and to create high quality retro  <a href="/news">news</a>,  <a href="/articles">articles</a>, <a href="/reviews">reviews</a> and have fun doing it.</p> 

      <img class="author" src="/img/lee-murray.png" alt="Lee Murray">
      <img class="author" src="/img/alex-murray.png" alt="Alex Murray">

  </div>

<div class="posts" data-layout="">
<h2>News</h2>
 <ul>
  {%- for post in collections.news | reverse -%}
    {% if loop.index0 < 3 %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">
        <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.alt }}"></img>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
      </a>
    </li>
     {% endif %}
  {%- endfor -%}
</ul>
<h2>Articles</h2>
 <ul>
  {%- for post in collections.article | reverse -%}
   {% if loop.index0 < 3 %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">
        <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.alt }}"></img>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
      </a>
    </li>
     {% endif %}
  {%- endfor -%}
</ul>
<h2>Reviews</h2>
 <ul>
  {%- for post in collections.reviews | reverse -%}
   {% if loop.index0 < 3 %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">
        <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.alt }}"></img>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
      </a>
    </li>
     {% endif %}
  {%- endfor -%}
</ul>
<h2>Games</h2>
 <ul>
  {%- for post in collections.games | reverse -%}
     {% if loop.index0 < 3 %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">
        <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.alt }}"></img>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
      </a>
    </li>
     {% endif %}
  {%- endfor -%}
</ul>
</div>
</div>
